| **Log parsing** | `line.split(" ")` with manual index arithmetic | 4 compiled regex patterns (`_RE_ERROR`, `_RE_USER`, `_RE_API`, `_RE_WARN`) |
| **Type safety** | None | Full type hints + docstrings on all public functions |
| **File handle** | Manual `f.close()` | `with open(...)` context manager |

